'''基斯托福·朱利葉斯·「克里斯」·洛克三世'''（{{lang-en|Christopher Julius "Chris" Rock III}}，{{bd|1965年|2月7日}}）是一名美國喜劇演員、編劇、導演及監製，以[[棟篤笑|棟篤笑]]出道，最著名的電影有《[[马达加斯加_(2005年电影)|荒失失奇兵]]》系列，曾於[[2005年電影|2005年]]主持[[第77屆奧斯卡金像獎|第77屆]][[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]。時隔11年，亦於[[2016年電影|2016年]]主持[[第88屆奧斯卡金像獎|第88屆]][[奧斯卡金像獎|奧斯卡金像獎]]。曾在第88届奥斯卡金像奖发表种族歧视言论，在舞台上公开嘲讽亚裔族群，并引来群众反弹。2014年《[[業內前五|業內前五]]》榮獲[[第86屆國家評論協會獎|第86屆國家評論協會獎]][[國家評論協會獎聚光燈獎|聚光燈獎]]。

==生平==
===早年===
洛克本名基斯托福·朱利葉斯·洛克三世（Christopher Julius Rock III），出生於[[美國|美國]][[南卡罗来纳州|南卡罗来纳州]][[安德鲁斯_(南卡罗来纳州)|安德鲁斯]]<ref name=yahoomovies>{{cite web|title=Chris Rock|publisher=[[Yahoo!_Movies|Yahoo! Movies]]|url=https://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800019115/bio|archivedate=2011-05-22|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110522142849/http://movies.yahoo.com/movie/contributor/1800019115/bio|accessdate=2018-06-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>；父親小基斯托福·朱利葉斯·洛克（Christopher Julius Rock Jr.）是一名貨車司機及報紙送遞員，母親Rosalie（閨姓Tingman）是一名老師及社工，專幫助智障者。<ref>{{cite news|title=Rolling Rock: Chris Rock Hits His Hollywood Stride|first=Cindy|last=Pearlman|url=https://www.rollingstone.com/artists/chrisrock/articles/story/5920132/rolling_rock_chris_rock_hits_his_hollywood_stride|work=Rolling Stone|date=January 29, 2001|accessdate=June 17, 2010|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20071214191014/http://www.rollingstone.com/artists/chrisrock/articles/story/5920132/rolling_rock_chris_rock_hits_his_hollywood_stride|archivedate=2007-12-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>洛克有兩名弟弟Tony和Jordan，兩人都在娛樂圈工作。<ref name="ToddBlue2009">{{cite book|author1=Anne M. Todd|author2=Rose Blue|author3=Corinne J. Naden|title=Chris Rock: Comedian and Actor|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=8Y_zke9klLEC&pg=PA21|date=1 January 2009|publisher=Infobase Publishing|isbn=978-1-4381-0074-6|access-date=2018-06-23|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609045533/https://books.google.com/books?id=8Y_zke9klLEC&pg=PA21|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.youtube.com/user/JayRockStar619|title=Jordan Rock: JayRockStar619's Channel|publisher=YouTube|date=August 31, 2006|accessdate=June 17, 2010|archive-date=2018-09-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919024131/https://www.youtube.com/user/JayRockStar619|dead-url=no}}</ref>

洛克出生沒多久後，一家搬了去紐約市[[布鲁克林区|布鲁克林区]]。<ref name="bravo">{{cite episode| title = Chris Rock| series = Inside the Actors Studio| serieslink = Inside the Actors Studio| network = [[Bravo_(US_TV_channel)|Bravo]]| airdate = March 13, 2007| season = 13| number = 6}}</ref>幾年後，洛克入學，但政府為了種族平等，安排洛克就讀一間大部分是白人的學校，洛克在那兒被白人同學欺凌及打罵。<ref name=bigger>{{cite news|url=http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1077/is_12_54/ai_55982855/|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130817230905/http://findarticles.com/p/articles/mi_m1077/is_12_54/ai_55982855/|dead-url=yes|archive-date=2013-08-17|title=Bigger, Better, And Hotter! Chris Rock Talks About Fame, Controversy And The Challenge Of Being No. 1|work=[[Ebony_(magazine)|Ebony]]|author=Chappell, Kevin|date=October 1999|accessdate=June 9, 2010}}</ref><ref name=king>{{cite news |url=http://premium.europe.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0102/12/lkl.00.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040924130836/http://premium.europe.cnn.com/TRANSCRIPTS/0102/12/lkl.00.html |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2004-09-24 |title=Chris Rock Discusses 'Down to Earth' |publisher=CNN |work=[[Larry_King_Live|Larry King Live]] |date=February 12, 2001 |accessdate=June 9, 2010 |df= }}</ref><ref name=show>{{cite news|url=http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,159947,00.html|title=Chris Rock Gets Show Based on Childhood|work=New York Post|date=June 18, 2005|author=Gallahue, Patrick|accessdate=June 13, 2010|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100629215425/http://www.foxnews.com/story/0,2933,159947,00.html|archive-date=2010-06-29|dead-url=yes}}</ref>到了中學James Madison High School，欺凌情況變得更差，其後洛克父母幫他退學，<ref name=show/>所以洛克最終是拿[[普通教育發展證書|GED]]的。跟著，洛克到不同的快餐店打工，但最後決定嘗試棟篤笑。

2008年，洛克參與了一個幫黑人尋根的[[PBS|PBS]]電視節目African American Lives 2，發現他祖先是從[[喀麥隆|喀麥隆]][[北部區_(喀麥隆)|北部區]]來的。<ref>Goffe, Leslie. [http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8117258.stm "Americans seek their African roots"] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/8117258.stm |date=20160104191932 }}, BBC, June 29, 2009.</ref>洛克亦有祖先曾是黑奴，在美國內戰時參加了美國有色人種部隊，幫北部打仗。洛克祖父Allen在1940年代，從南卡罗来纳州搬了去[[紐約市|紐約市]]，當了計程車司機及牧師。<ref>{{cite web|title=Chris Rock|url=https://www.pbs.org/wnet/aalives/profiles/rock.html|work=African American Lives 2|publisher=PBS|accessdate=December 19, 2010|archive-date=2017-07-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170720204300/http://www.pbs.org/wnet/aalives/profiles/rock.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>洛克則說他的表演方式，受到祖父傳道方式影響。

